<i>Miau, miau, miau</i>

239
00:11:12,104 --> 00:11:14,982
<i>Mentiroso macio,
Mentiroso quentinho</i>

240
00:11:14,992 --> 00:11:18,032
<i>Bolinha de trapaça</i>

241
00:11:18,042 --> 00:11:21,136
<i>Mentiroso feliz,
Mentiroso dorminhoco</i>

242
00:11:21,146 --> 00:11:24,315
<i>Trapaça, trapaça, trapaça</i>

243
